{"tid":1658031,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想問有無巴絲熟工傷/判傷","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:00:53.000Z","uid":17488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"948e06b610226bf23737e12a29b88b13f2d1f1a4","tid":1658031,"uid":17488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"我前個月去地盤做野個時俾電批扭到尾指甩骹<br />\n<br />\n去醫院駁返個下 醫生話有碎骨要開刀<br />\n<br />\n最後開完刀 佢幫我修補返韌帶同打左粒細釘落去<br />\n<br />\n（醫生話一世留係入面）到依家仲腫緊 渣筆都寫唔<br />\n<br />\n到字 <br />\n<br />\n到依家抖左兩個月 上網睇尾指整到計返百分比<br />\n（今年28歲）<br />\n<br />\n好似賠5萬幾倒<br />\n<br />\n今日見完物理治療師話咁既情況康復到可以返工需要兩個月倒<br />\n<br />\n我今個月30號就去勞工處判傷<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問如果我覺得太少去上訴 係味好大機會會俾<br />\n<br />\n人拖我幾年都攞唔到賠償 而且傷尾指上訴完賠償<br />\n<br />\n分別都唔會多好多<br />\n<br />\n同埋係咪需要押後個判傷日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n剛剛接觸地盤半年 對勞工條例好唔熟<br />\n<br />\n打上去問又俾得官方答案 希望有試過既巴絲可以<br />\n<br />\n解答我呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院做職業治療個時好多人會走埋黎問你係咪工傷 <br />\n<br />\n又問你洗唔洗索償個類 個堆人好鬼 所以我唔敢俾<br />\n<br />\n佢地知太多詳情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留低tg一個  求助於熱心巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yuk_lau1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyuk_lau1&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=79b2f82c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yuk_lau1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求  缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bdf7e0c08e38f464054f18f903e7aa58d60143fa","tid":1658031,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}